  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13093706/whistler-powder-skiing-838x350.jpg" alt="Whistler powder skiing" data-udi="umb://media/5ef46cbbe9ef41e8b0261a22851b7552" /></p>
<h2>Ski holiday - Snow Guarantee</h2>
<p><span>Our ski resorts are carefully chosen by our expert team, based on years of experience. We only feature resorts with reliable snow records, so you have the best chance of enjoying great conditions on your ski holiday. </span></p>
<p><span>But if there's no Snow? S’no problem! If you’ve booked a package holiday with us – including travel from the UK, accommodation and transport (flights, trains or self-drive) and the ski area of the resort you're staying in has less than 10% of their runs open due to lack of snow, we’ll organise transport to get you to and from a resort that has better skiing conditions for any affected days covered by your lift pass. Worried about losing out on unused lift passes or ski lessons that can’t go ahead? If you’ve booked these through us, we’ll refund you. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><a data-udi="umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c}" class="c-btn">Ski deals</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d}" class="c-btn">Ski holidays</a></span></p>
<h3><span>Terms &amp; Conditions: </span></h3>
<ul>
<li><span>The Inghams Snow Guarantee covers all of our ski holidays between December 2023 and April 2024. </span></li>
<li><span>Our Snow Guarantee is applicable from the arrival day, but we won’t organise transport until your first full ski day. </span></li>
<li><span>If fewer than 10% of runs are open in the resort you are staying in due to lack of snow, we will organise transport to and from a nearby resort that is open, free of charge, for any affected days covered by your lift pass. If there isn't an accessible glacier resort within two hours of your location, we won't be able to run a transport service. </span></li>
<li><span>If you’ve booked your ski lessons through Inghams, we’ll organise a refund for any ski lessons that can’t go ahead due to the resort being closed once you’ve arrived back in the UK. </span></li>
<li><span>If you’ve booked your lift passes through Inghams, we’ll do our best to organise replacement passes for the new resort if it isn’t covered by your existing pass. If we’re unable to do so, we’ll organise a refund once you've arrived back in the UK. </span></li>
<li><span>If you haven’t booked your ski lessons or lift passes through Inghams, we won’t be able to give you a refund, but we’ll do our best to help make alternative arrangements for your new resort and you’ll be able to use our transport services.</span></li>
</ul>
